[%@library reference_wrapper[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
reference_wrapper(T& t) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs a [`reference_wrapper] object that stores a reference to [`t].
[:zh_CN] 构造一个存储指代 [`t] 的引用的 [`reference_wrapper] 对象。
[exit:description]

[%@library reference_wrapper[![:en]constructor[:zh_CN]构造函数]]
[codeblock:declaration]
reference_wrapper(const reference_wrapper& x) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs a [`reference_wrapper] object that stores a reference to
[`x.get()].
[:zh_CN] 构造一个存储指代 [`x.get()] 的引用的 [`reference_wrapper] 对象。
[exit:description]
